Inferences

priceperlb is negatively corelated to stocks, totalprod,yeildpercol, numcol which means priceperlb is inversely proportional to all other attributes.

numcol has strong positive corelation among totalprod, stocks, prodvalue

stocks has positive corelation with totalprod

prodvalue has high positive corelation of 0.91 with totalprod
